column4: Walgreens and Microsoft partner to develop digital healthcare services
column5: Jan 15 Drugstore chain Walgreens Boots Alliance Inc and Microsoft Corp said on Tuesday they have entered a seven-year agreement to research and develop new methods of delivering healthcare services through digital devices.

column4: REFILE-UPDATE 1-German court throws out Qualcomm's latest patent case against Apple
column5: * Qualcomm  in earlier German case  won ban on some iPhone sales

column4: German court throws out Qualcomm's latest patent case against Apple
column5: FRANKFURT A patent lawsuit filed by Qualcomm Inc against Apple Inc was thrown out by a German court on Tuesday  in a reversal for the U.S. chipmaker after it won a recent court ban on the sale of some iPhones in the country.
